title: Characterization of Ceramics - Ronald E. Loehman
description:
Characterization of Ceramics - Ronald E. Loehman (Momentum Press, 2010).pdf

ISBN: 978-1-60650-194-8

Ceramics are, in general definition, materials that consist of man-made, inorganic, non-metallic solid material - either existing in a crystalline state or non-crystalline state. This book presents techniques along with views on trends in ceramics processing and advanced characterization technologies particularly appropriate to ceramics materials
